data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! LOCATION! Rare opportunity to purchase move-in ready home in Brantley Harbor which provides private boat ramp access to Lake Brantley! Beautifully remodeled 4-bedroom pool home with an amazing back yard oasis for entertaining and enjoying the Florida lifestyle. An extra large covered patio, gazebo with sitting area, pond and mature landscaping plus vinyl fence for privacy. There is even room for your boat or RV with the extended driveway.. Super low HOA fees of only $300 annually. This low-maintenance home has new energy-efficient windows, ceramic tile flooring throughout, newly-resurfaced pool, brick-paver deck, fountain and pump. Traditional formal living room and dining room. Kitchen open to family room. The kitchen and baths have been updated with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and wood cabinetry. The laundry room has been transformed into a great walk-in pantry. HVAC replaced about 8 years ago and roof (with 40-year warranty) replaced in 2005. Zoned for the best schools in Seminole County. NOTE: Appraiser measured living area as 1841 sq ft.
